OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1776172268
OL,3,CJury retires to consider verdict in a
OL,4,C'Miscarriage of Justice' rape trail
OL,6,FA jury has retired to consider
OL,7,Fverdicts in the trial of a man accused
OL,8,Fof a brutal stranger rape for which an
OL,9,Finnocent man spent 17 years in jail.
OL,11,FPaul Quinn denies carrying out the
OL,12,F2003 sex attack. He was only arrested
OL,13,Fnearly 20 years later after a DNA
OL,14,Fbreakthrough, and by then Andrew
OL,15,FMalkinson had already been wrongly
OL,16,Fconvicted and imprisoned.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
