PN,39502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1776172268
OL,3,CJury retires to consider verdict in a
OL,4,C'Miscarriage of Justice' rape trail
OL,6,FThe DNA sample from the vest top had
OL,7,Fbeen previously identified in 2007 as
OL,8,Fcoming from "Unknown Male 1", and
OL,9,Fanalysis had ruled out any link to Mr
OL,10,FMalkinson.
OL,12,FJurors at Manchester Crown Court began
OL,13,Fdeliberations on the afternoon of
OL,14,FMonday 13 April, as the trial entered
OL,15,Fits sixth week.
OL,17,FEarlier in the trial, John Price KC,
OL,18,Fprosecuting, told the court Mr
OL,19,FMalkinson, working as a security guard
OL,20,Fat a shopping centre, was the victim
OL,21,Fof a terrible miscarriage of justice.
OL,26,@pD@MOUpD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
