PN,39503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1776172268
OL,3,CJury retires to consider verdict in a
OL,4,C'Miscarriage of Justice' rape trail
OL,6,FThe victim, a mother-of-two in her
OL,7,F30s, was attacked as she walked home
OL,8,Fin the early hours of July 19, 2003.
OL,9,FShe suffered a violent assault,
OL,10,Fincluding a fractured cheekbone and
OL,11,Fother serious injuries, and was raped
OL,12,Ftwice.
OL,14,FNo DNA evidence ever linked Mr
OL,15,FMalkinson to the crime, but he was
OL,16,Fwrongly identified by three witnesses.
OL,18,FThe prosecution alleges the real
OL,19,Fperpetrator was father-of-six Quinn,
OL,20,Faged 29 at the time who lived a mile
OL,21,Ffrom the scene at the time.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1776172268
OL,3,CJury retires to consider verdict in a
OL,4,C'Miscarriage of Justice' rape trail
OL,6,FAdvances in DNA testing eventually
OL,7,Fproduced a billion-to-one match to
OL,8,FQuinn's profile left on the victim's
OL,9,Fclothing.
OL,11,FAlthough a DNA sample from the scene
OL,12,Fwas identified in 2007 as "Unknown
OL,13,FMale 1," it was not until 2022 that
OL,14,Fpolice matched it to Quinn, who had
OL,15,Fgiven a sample to police in 2012.
OL,17,FHe was arrested in 2022 and has denied
OL,18,Fany involvement.
OL,26,@tD@[OUuD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
