OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1776172268
OL,3,CJury retires to consider verdict in a
OL,4,C'Miscarriage of Justice' rape trail
OL,6,FDuring the trial, Quinn claimed his
OL,7,FDNA could have been transferred
OL,8,Finadvertently due to a highly
OL,9,Fpromiscuous lifestyle. He also
OL,10,Fadmitted to researching wrongful
OL,11,Fconvictions and police DNA retention.
OL,13,FQuinn, who moved from Little Hulton to
OL,14,FExeter in 2017, has pleaded not guilty
OL,15,Fto two counts of rape, two alternative
OL,16,Fcounts of indecent assault, grievous
OL,17,Fbodily harm, and attempting to choke
OL,18,For strangle his victim.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
