OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1776172268
OL,3,CJury retires to consider verdict in a
OL,4,C'Miscarriage of Justice' rape trail
OL,6,FHe also denies grievous bodily harm
OL,7,Fand attempting to choke or strangle
OL,8,Fhis victim to render her unconscious
OL,9,Fwhile he carried out the attack.
OL,11,FMr Malkinson, now 60, was released
OL,12,Ffrom prison in 2020 and had his
OL,13,Fconviction quashed by the Court of
OL,14,FAppeal.
OL,16,FThe jury will resume deliberations on
OL,17,FTuesday.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/6
